item.title: Again My Life - Ch. 117
item.description: A hot-blooded prosecutor, Kim Hee Wu,, was murdered and sunk into the ocean while chasing the tyrant who controlled Korea. But he meets a grim reaper who gives him a chance to relive and sends him back to when he was 18 years old. As a high schooler, Kim Hee Wu, prepares to punish the tyrant Jo Tae Sup.
